---
---

<section class="petition-blitz" id="petition-blitz">
  <div class="blitz-bg"></div>

  <div class="container blitz-content">
    <div class="blitz-alert animate-in">
      <span class="blitz-alert-icon">⚠️</span>
      <span class="blitz-alert-text" data-i18n="volunteer.blitz_alert">URGENT: PETITION DRIVE IN PROGRESS</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="blitz-headline animate-in" data-i18n="volunteer.blitz_headline">The Petition Blitz</h2>

    <div class="blitz-grid">
      <div class="blitz-context">
        <p class="blitz-text animate-in" data-i18n="volunteer.blitz_p1">
          Illinois election law intentionally punishes independent candidates to protect the two-party duopoly. The campaign is legally mandated to collect exactly 10,816 valid signatures just to appear on the ballot, while his machine-backed opponent bypassed this requirement entirely with just 697.
        </p>
        <p class="blitz-text animate-in" data-i18n="volunteer.blitz_p2">
          The political establishment will inevitably deploy armies of lawyers and bad-faith challenges to strike valid signatures. The campaign urgently needs volunteers to help gather a massive surplus of 40,000 to 50,000 signatures to survive these attacks.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="blitz-stats animate-in">
        <div class="blitz-stat">
          <span class="blitz-stat-number">10,816</span>
          <span class="blitz-stat-label" data-i18n="volunteer.blitz_required">Signatures required by law</span>
        </div>
        <div class="blitz-stat-arrow">→</div>
        <div class="blitz-stat blitz-stat-target">
          <span class="blitz-stat-number">50,000</span>
          <span class="blitz-stat-label" data-i18n="volunteer.blitz_needed">Signatures needed to survive challenges</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="blitz-cta animate-in">
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-cream btn-massive" data-i18n="volunteer.blitz_download">
        📋 Download Petition Sheets & Guidelines
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .petition-blitz {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .blitz-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange) 0%, var(--orange-dark) 100%);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .blitz-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* Alert Banner */
  .blitz-alert {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }

  .blitz-alert-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .blitz-alert-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .blitz-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  /* Grid */
  .blitz-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .blitz-text {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .blitz-text:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Stats */
  .blitz-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }

  .blitz-stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .blitz-stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #ffffff;
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .blitz-stat-target .blitz-stat-number {
    font-size: var(--text-5xl);
    text-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .blitz-stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    display: block;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .blitz-stat-arrow {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  /* CTA */
  .blitz-cta {
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .blitz-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .blitz-headline {
      font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    }

    .blitz-stat-target .blitz-stat-number {
      font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    }
  }
</style>
